{"tid":1427763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"留意到呢兩日民間自衛隊多左民意支持","createTime":"2019-08-07T07:39:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T16:56:56.000Z","uid":31215,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"85c48b8b9cb50579c360fd890108da76b32aa7eb","tid":1427763,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:39:54.000Z","msg":"因為北角荃灣都出現黑社會，全港市民都人心惶惶唔知幾時斬到自己嗰區<br />\n同時警察已經冇人信得過，知佢地報警都唔出現，出現左都係放犯<br />\n再見到勇武派做到野，打撚走黑社會，做左英雄，大快人心<br />\n不知不覺間<br />\n保護市民嘅期望，由公權機關，轉左去民間組織<br />\n如果條街有人搞事，有黑社會，開始有人期望黑衫大軍出黎趕走佢地，多過期望警察會出黎<br />\n<br />\n如果勇武派做好啲PR<br />\n當自己係美國隊長咁經營<br />\n保家衛族得黎對百性路人又溫柔啲<br />\n個民意基礎會持續狀大，到時啲人有事搵黑衫都唔搵警察<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519d75185edb88515c0be1de948389fdc9216b00","tid":1427763,"uid":272196,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:40:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d83613b038b7977cac97dca126bdd8a25a19e845","tid":1427763,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0a4190f0ebcd11e1b417514dedfa22739c612f","tid":1427763,"uid":107297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:56:26.000Z","msg":"一早講左勇武反黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6d524ceb296b7bf7b55d2320cf1c566d4702a4","tid":1427763,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e0a4190f0ebcd11e1b417514dedfa22739c612f","tid":1427763,"uid":107297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:56:26.000Z","msg":"一早講左勇武反黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:53:41.000Z","msg":"反黑係最拎到民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a02c2a92603ec39a5af11194127f43897e08f1a0","tid":1427763,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08